		<p>
			The Art and Design Studio (ADS) produces comics, fictions, games, and animated films to entertain and inform
			global audience.
		</p>
		<h1>Comic books</h1>
		<p>
			ADS comics are created to deliver messages. These comics are published online, accessible worldwide, and translated
			into multiple languages.
		</p>
		<p>
			The comics cover a broad range of topics from lifestyle, humour, to politics, etc. The paintings are made using 
			different art techniques. 
		</p>
		<h1>Flash fictions</h1>
		<p>
			ADS flash fictions are short, full-length fictional stories that are 3 to 5 pages long. These fictions are based on 
			reality. They cover a wide range of topics as the comics. All these fictions will be illustrated. These stories will 
			be published online. Most ADS stories will be written in English and Chinese.
		</p>
		<h1>Games</h1>
		<p>
			ADS games run in browsers, developed with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. These games will be based on the stories in comics,
			fictions, and animated films. Fans can visit brand websites to access these games.
		</p>
		<h1>Animation</h1>
		<p>
			ADS produces animated films and series. These films and series are developed in-house and based on true stories. 
			All the scripts and artwork belong to ADS. These films and series will be released on the ADS website, YouTube, and
			Bilibili.
		</p>
	</div>
